        <section class="panel home" data-section-name="home">
            <div class="main">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-offset-0">
                        <img src="images/logo.png" class="img-responsive">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1">
                        <h4>
                            A distributed information platform, focused on delivering immutability, and scalability to the masses.
                        </h4>
                        <br />
                        <div class="input-group" style="width:30%;margin:0 auto;">
                            <input type="text" id="hashloc" class="btn-round form-control" placeholder="Enter hash to view article">
                            <span class="input-group-btn">
                                <button class="btn btn-default btn-round" id="hashviewer" width="20" type="button">Go!</button>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/feed" class="btn btn-default btn-round btn-lg btn-cta">Explore News</a>
                        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                       <a href="/editor" class="btn btn-default btn-round btn-lg btn-cta">Post Your Own</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clicker clicker-bottom" onclick="javascript:$.scrollify.next();">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="panel product" data-section-name="product">
            <div class="inner col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0">
                <h1>About NewsChain</h1>
                <p>
                    The newschain platform empowers people through the properties of the merkle tree data structure and a distributed hash table to create a tamper-resistant archive of uploaded articles. We aim to harden information availability and integrity through crowdsourced volunteer nodes - the larger the number of participants the more difficult the archive becomes to eradicate. We also released the API that powers our platform with the MIT open-source license to democratize the improvement and extension of our technology.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="panel participate" data-section-name="participate">
            <div class="inner col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0">
                <h1>Use NewsChain</h1>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="clip col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                        Browse the accomplishments currently archived. Elevate your understanding to a higher level.<br />
                        <a href="/feed" class="btn btn-default btn-round btn-cta">Explore News</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="clip col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                        Send your cultural heritage through the generations. Leave your mark in history. <br />
                        <a href="/editor" class="btn btn-default btn-round btn-cta">Start Archiving</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="clip col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                        Help to protect our knowledge! Ensure that our descendants inherit our wisdom by hosting your own NewsChain node.<br />
                        <a href="/setup" class="btn btn-default btn-round btn-cta">Participate</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="panel about" data-section-name="about">
            <div class="clicker clicker-top" onclick="javascript:$.scrollify.move('#home');">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-up" aria-hidden="true"></span>
