            <div class="inner col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0">
                <h1>About Our Team</h1>
                <p>
                    We are a team of alumni software engineering majors from the University of Texas at Dallas with a passion for cutting-edge technology and humanitarian pursuits. This project was inspired by the main technological innovation of bitcoin: a distributed ledger called the blockchain. We wanted to apply our skills and comprehension of the technology towards a product that has the potential to make the world a better place.

                </p>
            </div>
